channel.title: Citelic 742 - Open Source Version
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/0bBBGST.png[/img]
Welcome to Citelic 742,
[b]Information:[/b] Name: Citelic Protocol: 742 Development Status: Active
[b]About:[/b] Me and Joris have been developing for quite some time, we felt like we should contribute it to the communities so they could move on to a higher server protocol instead of getting stuck on the 718's. This open source will stay on GitHub and I will continue on developing content on it.
[b]Media:[/b] [spoiler] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Qjmsigq.jpg[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/yLijemN.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/fEGoRMX.jpg[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Kif7fiO.jpg[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/sn1Ft9N.jpg[/img][/spoiler]
[b]Links:[/b] GitHub Repository: https://github.com/Citelic/Citelic-742
[b][i]Feel free to give us suggestions/feedback.[/i][/b] [/center]
